'''Chempat Engineered Defenses''', sometimes identified as '''Chepat''',<ref name="SWS" /> was a [[Starship/Legends|starship]] technology manufacturing corporation, specializing in the development and sale of shipboard [[Deflector shield/Legends|deflector shield]] projectors and [[Sensor/Legends|sensors]]. Chempat was jointly owned by the [[Corellian Engineering Corporation/Legends|Corellian Engineering Corporation]] and [[Kuat Drive Yards/Legends|Kuat Drive Yards]].<ref name="EGWT" />

